Strange

Can you follow these steps (or we can screenshare real quick and I can walk you through it):

1. Open up your developer tools (cmd+ctrl+i)
2. Go to the network tab 
3. Try to add the user
4. You'll see a new line in the network tab where the name is users; click on that, click the preview tab for the request, and expand the json blob, then the results field, then the error_details field
In the future we'll try to actually surface these details in the visible error message
